titleInfo.title: SHOWING THE THEATRE DU MARAIS, PARIS, 1676
PAINTING OF A THEATRE ATTRIBUTED TO BIBIENA

relatedItem.note: AND SINCE 1876 PRESERVED IN THE NATIONAL GALLERY, LONDON. The painting was once listed in the National Gallery Catalogue as representing "The Teatro Farnese, Parma and as being the work of Ferdinando Bibiena. There is little evidence as to the artist but it certainly does not represent the Teatro Farnese, Parma.
